fragment_downloaded_cb({"url": "hotdoc_markdown/gtkentry.html#gtk_entry_set_cursor_hadjustment", "fragment": "gtk_entry_set_cursor_hadjustment \nGtk.prototype.set_cursor_hadjustment \nGtk.Entry.set_cursor_hadjustment \nHooks up an adjustment to the cursor position in an entry so that when the cursor is moved the adjustment is scrolled to show that position. See gtk_scrolled_window_get_hadjustment for a typical way of obtaining the adjustment. \nThe adjustment has to be in pixel units and in the same coordinate system as the entry. \nParameters \na GtkEntry \nan adjustment which should be adjusted when the cursor is moved or NULL \nSince \nHooks up an adjustment to the cursor position in an entry so that when the cursor is moved the adjustment is scrolled to show that position. See Gtk.prototype.get_hadjustment for a typical way of obtaining the adjustment. \nThe adjustment has to be in pixel units and in the same coordinate system as the entry. \nParameters \na Gtk.Entry \nan adjustment which should be adjusted when the cursor is moved or null \nSince \nHooks up an adjustment to the cursor position in an entry so that when the cursor is moved the adjustment is scrolled to show that position. See Gtk.ScrolledWindow.get_hadjustment for a typical way of obtaining the adjustment. \nThe adjustment has to be in pixel units and in the same coordinate system as the entry. \nParameters \na Gtk.Entry \nan adjustment which should be adjusted when the cursor is moved or None \nSince \n"});